724484f-a.title: Manhattan: West End Avenue - 103rd Street (West)
724484f-a.text:
West End Avenue, S.E. corner of'103rd Street, showing the new 878
West End Avenue apartment building just completed. Compare this
with the companion picture, taken two months earlier, which bears
the detailed description of this scene.
May 16, 1923.
American Photo Service, Inc.
Gift of E. 1. Jenks.
